---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'OpenAI 推出团队共享智能体 Workspace Agents';
const description = 'OpenAI 推出 Workspace Agents，标志着企业级 AI 从个人工具向团队协作平台的战略转型。';
---

<Layout 
  title={title}
  description={description}
  type="article"
  publishedTime="2026-04-22"
  tags={["AI-Agents", "OpenAI", "ChatGPT", "Enterprise"]
}
>
  <article class="article-content">
    <h1 class="lang-content lang-zh active">OpenAI 推出团队共享智能体 Workspace Agents</h1>
    <h1 class="lang-content lang-en">OpenAI Launches Workspace Agents for Team Collaboration</h1>
    
    <time datetime="2026-04-22">2026-04-22</time>
    
    <div class="lang-content lang-zh active">
      <p>OpenAI 推出 Workspace Agents，标志着企业级 AI 从个人工具向团队协作平台的战略转型。这一举措直接回应了微软 Copilot 和谷歌 Workspace 在企业市场的竞争压力。</p>
      <p>基于 Codex 构建的智能体可在云端持续运行，即使团队成员离线也能处理销售跟进、软件审批等重复性工作。与 Slack 的深度集成意味着 OpenAI 正在争夺企业协作的核心入口。</p>
      <p>研究预览阶段的免费策略显示出 OpenAI 急于获取企业用户反馈。信用制定价模式一旦落地，将成为继 API 和订阅之后的第三条收入曲线。</p>
      <p><a href="https://openai.com/index/introducing-workspace-agents-in-chatgpt/" target="_blank">阅读原文</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="lang-content lang-en">
      <p>OpenAI's launch of Workspace Agents signals a strategic shift from personal AI tools to enterprise collaboration platforms. This move directly addresses competitive pressure from Microsoft Copilot and Google Workspace in the enterprise market.</p>
      <p>Built on Codex, these cloud-based agents continue operating even when team members are offline, handling repetitive tasks like sales follow-ups and software approvals. The deep Slack integration shows OpenAI is competing for the core entry point of enterprise collaboration.</p>
      <p>The free research preview strategy reveals OpenAI's urgency to gather enterprise user feedback. Once credit-based pricing kicks in, this will become the third revenue curve beyond APIs and subscriptions.</p>
      <p><a href="https://openai.com/index/introducing-workspace-agents-in-chatgpt/" target="_blank">Read the full article</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to articles</a>
  </article>
</Layout>
